<title>UK: OPEC BASKET PRICE STEADY AT $17.77 ON MONDAY.</title>
<headline>OPEC BASKET PRICE STEADY AT $17.77 ON MONDAY.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-08-12</dateline>
<text>
<p>The price of OPEC's basket of seven crudes was steady on Monday at $17.77 a barrel, the OPEC news agency said on Tuesday, quoting the OPEC Secretariat.</p>
<p>The basket comprises Algeria's Saharan Blend, Indonesia's Minas, Nigeria's Bonny Light, Saudi Arabia's Arabian Light, Dubai of the UAE, Venezuela's Tia Juana and Mexico's Isthmus.</p>
